The Synod Whisper Cell operating from the Sealed Route is directed by a commandant who has survived multiple prior interdiction attempts by relocating through the quarantine tunnels. Standard patrol actions have failed to fix a location long enough to strike decisively. The Midgaard postmaster has authorized a direct elimination writ against the commandant, contingent on confirmation that the whisper cell network has already been disrupted.
The Whisper Cell commandant has been eliminated and the command structure of the Sealed Route Synod operation has dissolved. Surviving cell operatives have scattered without the commandant's routing authority to reorganize. The postmaster has forwarded the elimination confirmation to the Violet Compact as evidence supporting the pending Synod charter revocation.
